---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - Bridge Builder in Computer Science" description="Learn about my journey from Xi'an to Berkeley and back, and my vision for democratizing CS education">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-teal-50 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        The <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-teal-600">Bridge Builder</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        My journey from Xi'an to Berkeley and back has shaped my mission: building bridges between cultures,
        technologies, and generations in computer science education.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Personal Narrative -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Story</h2>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Growing up in Xi'an, I discovered that the most meaningful learning happens when we build bridges—between
                cultures, between complex ideas and simple understanding, and between what technology can do and how it
                can help people. This realization would become the foundation of everything I do.
              </p>

              <p>
                My journey truly began when I had the opportunity to study at UC Berkeley during their summer session.
                Far from home, facing new challenges in a different educational system, I learned that adversity isn't
                just about overcoming obstacles—it's about using those experiences to build something better for others.
              </p>

              <p>
                When I returned to Xi'an Jiaotong University to pursue research in deep learning and explainable AI,
                I brought with me a unique perspective: the ability to see problems through both Eastern and Western
                educational lenses. This dual perspective became my superpower in creating solutions that work for
                diverse communities.
              </p>

              <p>
                But technology alone isn't enough. The real impact comes from education—from taking complex computer
                science concepts and making them accessible to everyone, starting with the youngest learners. This is
                why I created COMPSCI 0.10, a comprehensive course that has now reached over 350 elementary school students.
              </p>

              <p>
                Every challenge I've faced—from navigating cultural differences to explaining AI concepts to 8-year-olds—has
                reinforced my belief that the future of technology depends on our ability to democratize access to computer
                science education. I'm not just building AI systems; I'm building the next generation of thinkers who will
                use technology to solve humanity's greatest challenges.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-teal-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary-500">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">My Vision</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                To create a world where computer science education is accessible to everyone, where AI systems are
                explainable and beneficial to society, and where technology truly serves as a bridge between cultures
                and communities.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Core Values</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ml-3">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Accessibility</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Making CS education available to all ages and backgrounds</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-600 rounded-full"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ml-3">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Innovation</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Using creativity to solve complex problems</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ml-3">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Community</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Building inclusive learning environments</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-600 rounded-full"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ml-3">
                    <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Impact</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Creating measurable positive change</p>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Fun Facts</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li>• Fluent in Mandarin and English</li>
                <li>• Perfect ACSL competition score (12/12)</li>
                <li>• Only student from my province selected for the China Talented Youth Program</li>
                <li>• Built a study group that became a lifeline for international students</li>
                <li>• Can explain neural networks using playground analogies</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Interactive Timeline -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">My Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Key milestones that shaped my path in computer science</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-teal-400"></div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Timeline item 1 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg z-10">
              2020
            </div>
            <div class="ml-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Beginning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Started my computer science journey in Xi'an, discovering my passion for both technology and teaching.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline item 2 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg z-10">
              2022
            </div>
            <div class="ml-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Berkeley Experience</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Studied at UC Berkeley during summer session, achieving 4.0 GPA while building international study communities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline item 3 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg z-10">
              2023
            </div>
            <div class="ml-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Research & Teaching</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Began AI research at Xi'an Jiaotong University while creating COMPSCI 0.10 for elementary students.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline item 4 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg z-10">
              2024
            </div>
            <div class="ml-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Bridge Building</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Expanded impact to 350+ students, achieved perfect ACSL scores, and selected for China Talented Youth Program.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline item 5 -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg z-10">
              Now
            </div>
            <div class="ml-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex-1 border-2 border-primary-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Future Impact</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Continuing research in explainable AI while expanding educational initiatives and preparing for the next chapter.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials/Quotes -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Others Say</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Feedback from mentors, students, and collaborators</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M11.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.424-.768-.644-.648-.678.18-.036.648-.644.648-.678.426-.558.426-.66.426-.678 0-.36-.23-.618-.648-.618-.418 0-.648.258-.648.618 0 .36.23.618.648.618.418 0 .648-.258.648-.618 0-.36-.23-.618-.648-.618-.418 0-.648.258-.648.618 0 .36.23.618.648.618.418 0 .648-.258.648-.618"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">
            "Their ability to break down complex AI concepts and make them accessible to young students is remarkable.
            The COMPSCI 0.10 curriculum they developed shows true innovation in educational methodology."
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">— Research Supervisor</div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M11.192 15.757c0-.88-.23-1.618-.69-2.217-.326-.424-.768-.644-.648-.678.18-.036.648-.644.648-.678.426-.558.426-.66.426-.678 0-.36-.23-.618-.648-.618-.418 0-.648.258-.648.618 0 .36.23.618.648.618.418 0 .648-.258.648-.618 0-.36-.23-.618-.648-.618-.418 0-.648.258-.648.618 0 .36.23.618.648.618.418 0 .648-.258.648-.618"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic">
            "Working with them in our study group at Berkeley was inspiring. They have this unique ability to help
            everyone understand difficult concepts while building a supportive community."
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">— Fellow Student</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-teal-600 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Let's Build Bridges Together</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8">
        Whether you're interested in educational collaboration, research opportunities, or just want to connect,
        I'd love to hear your story and explore how we can work together.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-primary-600 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Get In Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>